snippet.title: The Double Down Update
snippet.description:
A mysterious entity and a familiar team of hired help threaten to destroy the Civilian's life's work—and the Civilian himself. He's prepared to expend every last corporate cog to stop them, including you.

The Double Down Update for TF2 Classic launches January 24th, 2025. Learn more at: https://tf2classic.com/double_down
